{"title":"游刘公岛感怀三首","authors":["沈毓珂"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"游刘公岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感怀三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈毓珂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眺望甲午海战处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疑是当年战火飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水天一色燃朝晖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休言忠骨沉沧海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪浪高镌无字碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰丁汝昌自尽室"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰东厢意慨然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军虽败寸心丹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜含愤自戕日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太后畅游万寿山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登山看旧炮台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山头巨炮昂然留，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲午风云举国愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潜艇于今飞导弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应欣一洗百年羞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}